name: Rnaseq
tagline: The repository will contain all necessary methods for doing rna-seq data analysis.
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
In this page I will describe my rna-seq pipeline.

### Experiment Design and Sequencing
Different tissue samples were collect and sequenced using Illumina HiSeq 2000 machine.


### Quality control
QC analysis was done using Fastqc and adapters were trimmed using cutadapt.
